1. *Vijest* o novom zakonu širi se brzo. (The *news* about the new law is spreading quickly.)
2. *Vijesti* sa današnjeg protesta su veoma važne. (*News* from today's protest is very important.)
3. Danas sam dobio *važnu vijest* od svog šefa. (Today I received an *important piece of news* from my boss.)
4. *Loše vijesti* o zdravlju moga prijatelja su me zabrinule. (*Bad news* about my friend's health worried me.)
5. Hvala ti što si mi preneo *dobru vijest* o uspehu mog sina. (Thank you for sharing with me the *good news* about my son's success.)
6. *Vijesti* su objavile detalje o incidentu koji se desio sinoć. (*The news* has published details about the incident that happened last night.)
7. Jutros nisam stigao da pogledam *vijesti* pre odlaska na posao. (This morning I didn't have time to watch *the news* before going to work.)
8. *Vijestima* se ne može uvek verovati, potrebno je proveriti informaciju. (You can't always trust *the news*, you need to fact-check the information.)
9. *Vijest* da će se održati koncert moje omiljene grupe me je obradovala. (The *news* that my favorite band is having a concert made me happy.)
10. *Vijest* o promeni rasporeda časova nas je iznenadila. (The *news* about the change in class schedule surprised us.)